<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Doctor Signup Pending</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c5aa0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #2c5aa0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #2c5aa0;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">HealthCare Platform</div>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="title">Application Received Successfully</h1>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear Dr. <%= doctorName %>,</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for your interest in joining our healthcare platform. We have successfully received your doctor registration application.</p>
            
            <div class="highlight">
                <strong>Application Status:</strong> Pending Review<br>
                <strong>Application ID:</strong> <%= applicationId %><br>
                <strong>Submitted Date:</strong> <%= submittedDate %>
            </div>
            
            <p>Your application is currently under review by our medical verification team. This process typically takes 2-3 business days as we carefully verify:</p>
            
            <ul>
                <li>Medical license and credentials</li>
                <li>Professional qualifications</li>
                <li>Identity verification</li>
                <li>Practice information</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>We will notify you via email once the review process is complete. You will receive either an approval confirmation or a request for additional information if needed.</p>
            
            <div class="highlight">
                <strong>What happens next?</strong><br>
                • Our team will review your submitted documents<br>
                • You'll receive an email notification within 2-3 business days<br>
                • Upon approval, you'll gain full access to the platform<br>
                • You can then start managing your practice and appointments
            </div>
            
            <p>If you have any questions or need to update your application, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for choosing our platform to serve your patients.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The Healthcare Platform Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>If you need assistance, contact us at support@healthcareplatform.com</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Healthcare Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>